schools.name: Clifford O. Pete Findlay Middle School

data.description: Beautiful Updated 2 story home in a gated community that offers Park, BBQ Areas, community pool and walking trails. Located near Schools, Shopping and Entertainment this home is sure to catch your eye. Brand New Shutters throughout!  Kitchen offers all appliances, a pantry and Granite counter tops overlooking the family room! With 3 bedrooms upstairs and 1 downstairs. The Primary Bathroom has double sinks, Walk in closet and separate shower and tub! Come and see this property today!
